Package: mydns
Architecture: any
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}, adduser, lsb-base (>= 4.1)
Description: SQL-backed authoritative DNS server with Cloudflare mirroring
 MyDNS serves authoritative DNS zones directly from MySQL databases. This
 fork adds Cloudflare zone mirroring, IPv6-aware utilities, reply-cache
 fixes, and multi-host database failover while keeping the daemon simple
 and fast.
